metadata.title: Rubbermaid Commercial Executive Series Lobby Pro Dustpan with Long Handle, Black (FG253104BLA), 5" x 12-3/4" x 11-1/4"
features: Sturdy plastic won't stain, discolor, or absorb odors
description: The Rubbermaid Commercial Upright Dust Pan features a stylish long handle dust pan design for easy clean-up. The upright dust pan is self-opening and closing and includes an adjustable handle grip. The Rubbermaid dust pan is designed with rear wheels for reduced wear and is constructed of sturdy plastic that won't stain, discolor, or absorb odors. These dust pans are ideal for use in malls, restaurants, lobbies and other locations with heavy traffic.
